import React from "react" import Title from "./Components/Title" import Die from "./Components/Die" export default function App() { function initDiceArr() { const diceArr = [] for (let i = 0; i < 10; i++) { diceArr.push(Math.floor(Math.random() * 10) + 1) } return diceArr } return (
<div className="game-container"> <Die value="1" /> <Die value="2" /> <Die value="3" /> <Die value="4" /> <Die value="5" /> <Die value="6" /> <Die value="7" /> <Die value="8" /> <Die value="9" /> <Die value="10" /> </div> <button>ROLL</button> </main> ) }
